snippet.title: Orcs Must Die! Deathtrap - Gameplay Overview Trailer
snippet.description:
Think you've got what it takes to become a legendary War Mage?

On January 28th, step into Orcs Must Die! Deathtrap and forge your path to total orc destruction.🏰💣

With a massive arsenal of traps, powerful abilities, and endless mayhem...what more could you ask for?

(Well, maybe the most handsome War Mage to ever grace The Order—but we got you covered on that!)
